data.description: Amazing Belleview Home Ready for You! Priced to Sell!  Welcome to your dream home in Belleview, FL!  This fantastic property is priced to sell and offers one of the region's lowest prices per square foot. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!    Key Features:    3 Beds, 2 Baths, 1892 sqft: Spacious, elegant, and designed for comfort.    One house is featured with 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and one carport. The other one is featured with 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, attached garage and independent entrance. CANNOT BE SOLD SEPARATELY.    1-acre lot: Unwind in your expansive backyard oasis, offering ample space for your lifestyle and imagination.  New Stainless Steel Appliances: A modern kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances for culinary adventures.  Versatile Garage Space: A massive garage with abundant storage beckons creativity – envision your dream workshop or consider transforming it into a lucrative in-law kitchenette for additional rental income!  Priced to Sell: An unbeatable opportunity to make this your forever home.  This isn't just a house; it's a canvas for your dreams. Don't miss out on the chance to own this gem
